Name: Keooudorn Lily Phothisane
Description:
Keooudorn died from blunt force injuries to the neck and head. Her body had also been burned.

> On May 8, 1997, Mark Antonio Profit, 33, was found guilty of the strangulation death the previous May of prostitute Renee Bell, who's body was found floating in a creek in Theodore Wirth Park in Minneapolis. Profit was also found guilty of two counts of the sexual attack on another woman.
> 
> Profit, who has spent nearly one-half of his life in prison for violence and sexual assaults, was known as the "Wirth Park Killer". According to a county attorney Profit has been out of prison for only a year since he was 15 years old.
> 
> Police believe Bell was the first of four victims in a four-month serial killing spree. His three other suspected victims are, Deborah LaVoie, 43, whose burned body was found June 3 in Wirth Park; Avis Warfield, 36, found June 19 near the park, and Keooudorn Photisane, 21, found July 29 in bushes near a bike path and the park's golf course.

Keooudorn was born on 2nd January 1975 and was killed on 20th July 1996.

Name: Martine Bohn
Description:
Martine was murdered soon after her disappearance on 21st July, 1996 by an unidentified serial killer, dubbed by the media as "The Butcher of Mons."

> It was March 22, 1997. Bags containing body parts were discovered between Mons and Cuesmes. This is the start of the Mons carver case. Five victims are attributed to him: Carmelina Russo, Martine Bohn, Jacqueline Leclercq, Nathalie Godart and Begonia Valencia.

Martine was a transient transgender woman and former sex worker from France who worked at seedy bars in both France and Belgium. Following her disappearance, police learned that she had lost all contact with her family and hadn’t kept many friends during her life. When her partial remains were found floating in the Haine River [in July 1997], investigators deduced that the killer had sliced off her breasts after learning that Bohn was trans. This provided further proof that the killer was motivated by sex.
